# STREAMING::IPL_GROUP_SWAP_IS_ACTIVE

## Summary
: returns true if a swap is active

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
indicates that there is a scripted IPL group swap active
